  "remarks": "Armament Industries Group (AIG) was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: AIG manufacturers and services a variety of small arms and light weapons, including large- and medium-calibre guns and related technology. AIG conducts the majority of its procurement activity through Hadid Industries Complex. The Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
